Wait, wait, uh, what?

758
01:08:19.926 --> 01:08:24.762
Vilma called me last night and asked
about your experimental treatment.


759
01:08:25.565 --> 01:08:27.665
You're jeopardizing my career.

760
01:08:27.667 --> 01:08:30.635
Look, I'm sorry, I just...
I had to give her a reason


761
01:08:30.637 --> 01:08:32.904
for not coming back to the sessions.
I mean, she wouldn't let me go


762
01:08:32.906 --> 01:08:34.038
unless... I had to.

763
01:08:35.108 --> 01:08:36.407
I promise it won't happen again.

764
01:08:36.409 --> 01:08:38.676
Mike, this was a bad idea.

765
01:08:39.913 --> 01:08:42.247
I, I, I can't trust you anymore.

766
01:08:42.249 --> 01:08:45.116
No, no, no, no, no.
Please, Angie.


767
01:08:45.118 --> 01:08:49.454
You gotta help me.
You're my last chance to survive.


768
01:08:52.993 --> 01:08:54.726
I'm willing to take the risks.

769
01:09:03.603 --> 01:09:08.139
Did you, uh, send my dad
to Vilma after he was diagnosed?


770
01:09:08.141 --> 01:09:12.744
I recommended him to go,
but you know how proud he is.


771
01:09:21.054 --> 01:09:22.954
Are you okay?

772
01:09:22.956 --> 01:09:24.188
Phew.

773
01:09:24.190 --> 01:09:26.090
I told you the treatment
is aggressive.


774
01:09:46.546 --> 01:09:48.146
I hope you don't mind.
I took one of yours.


775
01:09:55.789 --> 01:10:00.091
Now, I didn't know you went to
therapy right after you got diagnosed.


776
01:10:00.093 --> 01:10:03.661
Shrinks are for crazy people.

777
01:10:03.663 --> 01:10:06.564
You went to Vilma's therapy group
though, didn't you?


778
01:10:06.866 --> 01:10:07.932
Hmm?

779
01:10:11.504 --> 01:10:13.404
I don't believe I know her.

780
01:10:13.406 --> 01:10:15.440
Did you get to know
Piedad Lopez?


781
01:10:15.442 --> 01:10:17.408
You know, the one with all
the plastic surgery.


782
01:10:20.347 --> 01:10:21.813
Did they tell you
about the Chain?


783
01:10:26.086 --> 01:10:27.618
What did they tell you about it?

784
01:10:27.620 --> 01:10:30.154
Michael dear, guess what?

785
01:10:30.156 --> 01:10:32.423
I found you another shirt.

786
01:10:33.360 --> 01:10:35.493
I don't know how
that other one just vanished.


787
01:10:36.262 --> 01:10:38.429
Like socks in a dryer,
I suppose.


788
01:10:39.766 --> 01:10:41.499
I didn't know you smoked, too.

789
01:10:43.036 --> 01:10:47.171
Anyway, I got one for you, too.
They were on sale.


790
01:10:49.342 --> 01:10:50.708
Why don't you try it on?

791
01:10:52.278 --> 01:10:53.945
I think it'll look
lovely on you.


792
01:11:27.514 --> 01:11:30.214
Like I said,
your life, your rules.


793
01:11:30.216 --> 01:11:32.116
That's how the Chain works.

794
01:11:32.118 --> 01:11:35.520
You and your assigned link
can figure all the details out.


795
01:11:37.557 --> 01:11:40.091
Here's the contact information
you'll need.


796
01:12:03.550 --> 01:12:08.219
Yes, good morning, ma'am,
I'd like to book suite 1010 for tonight.


797
01:12:10.423 --> 01:12:12.623
Mmm-hmm. Thank you.

798
01:12:21.167 --> 01:12:23.768
Relax. You need to relax.

799
01:12:26.940 --> 01:12:29.874
- Mike, hello?
- Shit, that's my wife.


800
01:12:36.015 --> 01:12:39.317
Hey, sweetheart, ahem,
do you need anything?


801
01:12:40.620 --> 01:12:42.453
Sorry to interrupt.

802
01:12:42.455 --> 01:12:46.657
This is Dr. Ryan, my father's physician,
and Dr. Ryan, this is my wife, Sarah.


803
01:12:46.659 --> 01:12:48.759
Nice to meet you.

804
01:12:48.761 --> 01:12:51.529
- How is he?
- Stable.


805
01:12:51.531 --> 01:12:54.832
But there isn't much more
we can do for him.


806
01:12:57.504 --> 01:13:01.072
Call me if you need
anything else.


807
01:13:01.074 --> 01:13:03.140
It was nice to meet you, too.

808
01:13:23.196 --> 01:13:24.328
Um...

809
01:13:25.231 --> 01:13:28.032
Do you mind if we talk at home.

810
01:13:28.034 --> 01:13:29.967
I'm just kind of busy.

811
01:13:34.707 --> 01:13:36.007
I called Rebecca.

812
01:13:37.510 --> 01:13:39.944
The practice has been closed
for weeks now.


813
01:13:41.481 --> 01:13:44.048
All those night surgeries,
all of that...


814
01:13:44.984 --> 01:13:47.051
paperwork that
you had to finish...


815
01:13:48.955 --> 01:13:49.921
Lies.

816
01:13:51.491 --> 01:13:53.791
I kind of really
fucked up, babe.


817
01:13:56.629 --> 01:13:58.062
Are you having an affair?

818
01:13:59.399 --> 01:14:02.166
No. No. Absolutely not.

819
01:14:04.404 --> 01:14:06.137
Please, just be honest with me.

820
01:14:11.144 --> 01:14:12.310
My father...

821
01:14:14.380 --> 01:14:16.180
is pretending to be sick.

822
01:14:16.182 --> 01:14:17.982
He's been lying to us all
since the beginning.


823
01:14:17.984 --> 01:14:20.384
He told me himself.
He just wanted me to come back here.


824
01:14:21.020 --> 01:14:22.653
I was sick.

825
01:14:23.489 --> 01:14:24.855
But I'm getting better.

826
01:14:24.857 --> 01:14:26.691
That's why Dr. 
Ryan was here.

827
01:14:26.693 --> 01:14:30.061
But I... I didn't want to tell you
because I didn't want you to worry.


828
01:14:30.363 --> 01:14:31.662
Okay?

829
01:14:33.132 --> 01:14:35.399
But someone is going
to kill me if I don't stop them.


830
01:14:35.401 --> 01:14:39.203
And I'm pretty sure my father has information
about the Chain. He just won't tell me.


831
01:14:40.106 --> 01:14:41.172
Mike.

832
01:14:42.675 --> 01:14:44.742
You need to go to therapy.
You're losing your mind.


833
01:14:44.744 --> 01:14:46.210
Don't you ever say that.

834
01:14:46.212 --> 01:14:47.878
Get away from me!

835
01:15:29.722 --> 01:15:32.757
Excuse me, I have a reservation.

836
01:15:32.759 --> 01:15:35.292
Yeah. First time staying
with us, sir?


837
01:15:35.294 --> 01:15:36.927
Uh, yeah.

838
01:15:49.809 --> 01:15:51.742
You look pretty different
with the beard.


839
01:15:52.712 --> 01:15:53.911
You look better now.

840
01:15:56.949 --> 01:15:59.884
Welcome, Mr. Coleman.
It is suite 1010.


841
01:16:01.654 --> 01:16:02.920
Enjoy your stay.

842
01:16:13.766 --> 01:16:15.099
Help me.

843
01:16:17.336 --> 01:16:19.503
Mike, help me.

844
01:16:26.846 --> 01:16:28.813
Piedad, there's nothing
I can do for you.


845
01:16:30.383 --> 01:16:31.549
You're dead.

846
01:17:01.380 --> 01:17:05.182
Well, well, well,
look who we have here.


847
01:17:05.184 --> 01:17:07.351
Returning to the crime scene,
Dr. Coleman.


848
01:17:07.353 --> 01:17:08.385
Uh...

849
01:17:15.128 --> 01:17:19.029
- Do you mind if we go talk someplace else?
- Sure.


850
01:17:19.031 --> 01:17:21.265
There's a bar nearby.
I think you know it.


851
01:17:22.368 --> 01:17:24.168
<i>The Chain?</i>

852
01:17:24.169 --> 01:17:25.969
I know it sounds crazy,
but it's true.


853
01:17:25.972 --> 01:17:27.638
You need to stop them.

854
01:17:27.640 --> 01:17:30.508
Hello, stranger.
What can I get you?


855
01:17:30.510 --> 01:17:31.575
A coke, please.

856
01:17:31.577 --> 01:17:34.044
- I'll have the same.
- Two cokes.


857
01:17:34.046 --> 01:17:35.613
Is your friend
joining you today?


858
01:17:36.082 --> 01:17:36.947
Excuse me?

859
01:17:36.949 --> 01:17:38.382
The lady
that you always come with.


860
01:17:41.621 --> 01:17:44.388
No, no, she's not coming today.

861
01:17:44.390 --> 01:17:46.957
Oh, be right back.

862
01:17:52.365 --> 01:17:53.364
So...

863
01:17:54.801 --> 01:17:56.667
you know how to find
who killed Miss Lopez.


864
01:17:56.669 --> 01:18:00.905
Yes. Uh, Vilma. You have to
investigate Vilma, the therapist, okay?


865
01:18:00.907 --> 01:18:02.273
Everyone who's been to...

866
01:18:12.084 --> 01:18:16.687
I went back to the hotel to try
and find Piedad's notebook, okay.


867
01:18:16.689 --> 01:18:20.291
She wrote down everything. Okay.
There's bound to be some names in there.


868
01:18:20.293 --> 01:18:23.294
We searched her room.
It was empty.


869
01:18:24.697 --> 01:18:27.798
Okay. Sure.

870
01:18:27.800 --> 01:18:32.770
Look, Mike, I need you to come down
in the morning. Give a statement.


871
01:18:32.772 --> 01:18:35.639
If everything you're saying is
true, we will help you.


872
01:18:36.776 --> 01:18:38.309
But you gotta
tell us everything.


873
01:18:39.212 --> 01:18:40.911
And stop playing detective.

874
01:18:44.417 --> 01:18:47.585
Oh, my God, that's him.

875
01:18:54.861 --> 01:18:56.594
Hey, stop!

876
01:18:56.596 --> 01:18:57.928
I don't want to die anymore!

877
01:19:06.205 --> 01:19:07.771
You saw that, right?

878
01:19:07.773 --> 01:19:10.774
You saw that it wasn't my fault.
He just came out of nowhere.


879
01:19:10.776 --> 01:19:11.942
Look, just get back in your car.

880
01:19:11.944 --> 01:19:13.444
- I know, but it wasn't my fault.
- I'm a doctor.


881
01:19:13.446 --> 01:19:14.678
Call an ambulance!

882
01:19:15.147 --> 01:19:16.113
Okay.

883
01:20:33.626 --> 01:20:35.726
- There's no need to keep pretending, Father.
- Hmm?


884
01:20:38.064 --> 01:20:39.430
I know you're my link.

885
01:20:40.132 --> 01:20:41.832
How was your day, son?

886
01:20:41.834 --> 01:20:43.067
I hope you're hungry.

887
01:20:43.069 --> 01:20:45.469
Starving. Quite a busy day.

888
01:20:46.172 --> 01:20:49.473
Well, Sarah is a gem.

889
01:20:49.475 --> 01:20:53.310
She went to the market, bought a big duck.
She's been cooking all day.


890
01:20:53.312 --> 01:20:54.278
Hmm.

891
01:21:12.732 --> 01:21:13.764
I'm sorry.

892
01:21:16.402 --> 01:21:17.468
For everything.

893
01:21:20.973 --> 01:21:25.109
I haven't been myself lately.
And I'm gonna put an end to it.


894
01:21:28.581 --> 01:21:29.613
I love you.

895
01:21:35.955 --> 01:21:38.255
You better get
your shit together, Mike.


896
01:21:40.159 --> 01:21:42.359
I don't even know
who you're becoming.


897
01:21:45.698 --> 01:21:48.365
I'm gonna prove to you
that my father is faking.


898
01:21:50.169 --> 01:21:51.769
He wants to kill me.

899
01:21:55.508 --> 01:21:56.540
Stop it.

900
01:21:59.412 --> 01:22:00.411
You'll see.

901
01:22:08.287 --> 01:22:12.022
These potatoes are out of this world.
You used thyme, right?


902
01:22:12.024 --> 01:22:13.857
Um, yeah, I did. Um...

903
01:22:13.859 --> 01:22:18.095
But the key was to precook them in the
microwave before I put them in the oven.


904
01:22:18.097 --> 01:22:21.265
Really? I never would
have thought of that.


905
01:22:23.235 --> 01:22:26.036
Mom, let him do it.

906
01:22:26.038 --> 01:22:30.507
Your dad can't
coordinate his hands well enough.


907
01:22:30.509 --> 01:22:33.911
Mom, if he can hit you,
he can feed himself.


908
01:22:34.580 --> 01:22:36.480
Mike!

909
01:22:36.482 --> 01:22:38.449
You can feed yourself,
can't you, Father?


910
01:22:39.385 --> 01:22:40.584
Show 'em.

911
01:22:40.586 --> 01:22:43.654
Son, let's just have
a nice family dinner.


912
01:22:44.623 --> 01:22:45.789
Mike, stop it.

913
01:22:46.659 --> 01:22:48.692
What are you doing?

914
01:22:48.694 --> 01:22:50.427
We're not helping him
get better, Mom.


915
01:22:51.697 --> 01:22:53.764
Eat.

916
01:22:53.766 --> 01:22:55.666
He can't do it by himself.

917
01:22:55.668 --> 01:22:57.734
Yes, he can. I've seen it.

918
01:22:57.736 --> 01:22:59.903
Come on, just a little bite.

919
01:23:02.174 --> 01:23:04.808
Sarah spent all day
working on this meal for you.


920
01:23:07.513 --> 01:23:09.813
Come on.
We both know you can do it.


921
01:23:14.053 --> 01:23:15.319
Eat!

922
01:23:30.069 --> 01:23:32.836
Sometimes you just gotta be a
little hard on him for his own good.


923
01:23:32.838 --> 01:23:34.204
Right, Ma?

924
01:23:35.007 --> 01:23:36.373
That's what he always said.

925
01:23:44.049 --> 01:23:45.249
Phew!

926
01:23:50.923 --> 01:23:54.858
Sarah, would you take care of
Michael tomorrow, around 4:00?


927
01:23:54.860 --> 01:23:58.195
I'd really like to go to
Claire's daughter's baby shower.


928
01:23:58.197 --> 01:23:59.530
I can do it, Mom.

929
01:24:00.933 --> 01:24:02.332
Sarah's got rehearsals.

930
01:24:02.334 --> 01:24:03.967
You know,
the kid's recital's on Friday.


931
01:24:03.969 --> 01:24:05.802
I have zero patients tomorrow.

932
01:24:07.773 --> 01:24:09.940
I don't mind, really.

933
01:25:05.331 --> 01:25:07.231
There's some pudding left
in the fridge, if you're hungry.


934
01:25:07.233 --> 01:25:09.399
Thanks, Mom.
Have fun. Don't worry.


935
01:25:30.689 --> 01:25:31.722
Father.

936
01:25:54.046 --> 01:25:55.445
Father, where are you?

937
01:26:55.674 --> 01:26:57.107
Father, what are you doing?

938
01:26:57.109 --> 01:26:58.575
Following your instructions.

939
01:26:58.577 --> 01:27:00.911
It'll look like you hit
your head against the tub.


940
01:27:00.913 --> 01:27:02.045
It was an accident.

941
01:27:03.749 --> 01:27:06.416
I don't want to die anymore.
There's a cure for me.


942
01:27:06.418 --> 01:27:08.318
Oh, there's no cure, you fool.

943
01:27:24.470 --> 01:27:27.104
Come on.

944
01:27:28.674 --> 01:27:31.908
Now we're even!
You're never gonna see Mom or me again,


945
01:27:31.910 --> 01:27:34.144
or that fucking nurse
of yours, do you hear me?


946
01:27:40.619 --> 01:27:41.918
Oh!

947
01:27:59.705 --> 01:28:01.037
How are you feeling?

948
01:28:05.611 --> 01:28:08.178
- My father...
- Mike.


949
01:28:08.180 --> 01:28:12.048
It's gonna be difficult,
but you need to try to remain calm, okay.


950
01:28:12.618 --> 01:28:14.718
Your father passed away.

951
01:28:14.720 --> 01:28:18.822
He fell and hit his head
and drowned in the bathtub.


952
01:28:18.824 --> 01:28:23.160
You had a heart attack,
when you were trying to help him.


953
01:28:23.162 --> 01:28:24.661
We almost lost you.

954
01:28:26.799 --> 01:28:28.665
Dr. Ryan came
to see you last night.


955
01:28:28.667 --> 01:28:31.835
She said that you need to rest.
No more craziness.


956
01:28:31.837 --> 01:28:34.905
Just a couple of days in bed.
Avoid stress at all costs.


957
01:28:35.507 --> 01:28:36.673
You got it?

958
01:28:37.843 --> 01:28:38.975
Hmm.

959
01:28:40.746 --> 01:28:43.547
Sarah, I don't want
to be here anymore.


960
01:28:46.051 --> 01:28:49.286
I want to get out of this house and
I want to go back to San Francisco.


961
01:28:52.024 --> 01:28:53.757
You get better.

962
01:28:53.759 --> 01:28:56.760
Rest a couple of days,
and then we'll go wherever you want.


963
01:29:00.232 --> 01:29:02.199
I have to go now.

964
01:29:02.201 --> 01:29:05.969
Your mom is alone at the funeral home.
I'll be back, okay.


965
01:30:37.296 --> 01:30:38.328
Yeah, Detective Darcy.

966
01:30:39.598 --> 01:30:41.031
Yeah, I'd like
to make my statement.


967
01:30:57.282 --> 01:30:58.782
What is she doing here?

968
01:30:59.351 --> 01:31:01.017
Mike, please, sit down.

969
01:31:09.795 --> 01:31:10.994
What the fuck is this?

970
01:31:13.632 --> 01:31:17.367
Isn't it clear?
Exactly what you wanted.


971
01:31:17.369 --> 01:31:20.670
She's killing you,
making it look like a natural death.


972
01:31:20.672 --> 01:31:25.141
Digitoxin doesn't leave a trace in
the blood stream. You know that.


973
01:31:25.677 --> 01:31:27.277
"Your life. Your rules."

974
01:31:28.580 --> 01:31:29.813
Mike.

975
01:31:32.117 --> 01:31:34.284
Mike, Piedad used you.

976
01:31:34.286 --> 01:31:39.456
She invited you to the Chain because
Vilma didn't let her link to help her.


977
01:31:39.458 --> 01:31:43.660
So, she decided to rearrange
things behind our backs.


978
01:31:43.662 --> 01:31:48.231
In order to be helped by the Chain,
you must have Vilma's and my permission.


979
01:31:48.233 --> 01:31:51.901
I make sure the patients medical
conditions are irreversible.


980
01:31:51.903 --> 01:31:54.471
And she makes sure they're
ready for the final step.


981
01:31:55.474 --> 01:31:57.407
Obviously,
she didn't have either.


982
01:31:58.844 --> 01:32:00.377
So the treatment was a lie.

983
01:32:02.914 --> 01:32:05.782
You should be thankful
to Dr. Ryan.


984
01:32:05.784 --> 01:32:09.786
After you and Piedad messed up,
I stopped the Chain.


985
01:32:09.788 --> 01:32:12.122
But she still wanted
to help you.


986
01:32:12.124 --> 01:32:15.358
We need to stop this
until it calms down.


987
01:32:15.360 --> 01:32:16.559
It's all over the place.

988
01:32:16.561 --> 01:32:18.228
<i>I can't abandon him now,</i>

989
01:32:18.230 --> 01:32:20.897
I brought him into this.
He's expecting a link to help him die.


990
01:32:20.899 --> 01:32:23.733
<i>I don't give a damn about him.
He is not our problem.</i>


991
01:32:25.303 --> 01:32:29.205
It was the only way
I could follow your rules.


992
01:32:30.842 --> 01:32:33.743
The truth is
that there is no cure.


993
01:32:33.745 --> 01:32:38.281
Your heart is already very weak. One more
dose and you will die of a heart attack.


994
01:32:38.283 --> 01:32:40.216
No one will ever know.

995
01:32:47.459 --> 01:32:48.758
Did you get all that?

996
01:32:50.796 --> 01:32:52.896
It's a full confession.
Arrest them.


997
01:32:55.534 --> 01:32:57.033
Mike, who are you talking to?

998
01:32:58.603 --> 01:33:00.537
This is Detective Darcy
of the LAPD.


999
01:33:03.375 --> 01:33:05.475
There's no one there, Mike.

1000
01:33:13.285 --> 01:33:15.952
I was being investigated
by insurance companies.


1001
01:33:17.656 --> 01:33:19.189
There's pictures, there's...

1002
01:33:21.460 --> 01:33:22.826
