1021
01:35:23.782 --> 01:35:26.416
<i>If Mom finds out
about this,</i>


1022
01:35:26.418 --> 01:35:29.185
she's going to agree to send
you to a fucking nursing home.


1023
01:35:31.389 --> 01:35:33.556
